        <p>For deity jewellery, the team helps customers think through idol height, face or head width, crown space, necklace drop, waist placement, altar clearance and deity-specific compatibility. For dance jewellery, the focus is on Bharatanatyam and Kuchipudi stage use, set completeness, comfort, visibility and durability.</p>
        <h2 style="color:#8b1c1c;font-size:28px;margin:34px 0 12px;">What We Specialise In</h2>
